Package: wellr
Title: Utilities for Working Plate Based Data
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Brady",
           family = "Johnston",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brady.johnston@me.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6301-2269"))
Description: {wellr} provides a range of utility functions for working with 
    plate-based data from microtitre plates. Working with column IDs, row 
    numbers and letters and transforming between a matrix and a data frame are 
    all made simpler by {wellr}.
